attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Quality and Care hallmark this gut renovated 3 bedroom condo with bonus office/mudroom that can be converted to legal 4th bedroom. Located perfectly between M Street Park, Marine Park, M street Beach and L Street. This newly renovated home features a 3 zone Heat Pump for high efficiency heating and cooling, wood clad Anderson windows, 8 foot slider to private outdoor patio off the open concept Livingroom/Dining room/Kitchen. The first floor offers 2 bedrooms with soaring 10 foot ceilings each with attached bathroom, ducted condenser heat pump, full size LG laundry, 2 common closets and mudroom/office/4th bedroom. The lower level living space includes a wet bar, Thermador professional appliances, large pantry, 2 extra closets for storage and a bedroom with full bathroom. Every detail has been considered including Garage prewired for EV Phase 2 AC Car Charger and patio plumbed with gas line for grille.
